zientes empirisches Werkzeug zur Analyse der heutigen Medienlandschaft.  afunded by Hans-Böckler-Stiftung  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 0aSocial media. 4aBild. 4aBildtheorie. 4aBildung. 4aBildwissenschaft. 4aComputerspiele. 4aFacebook. 4aGames. 4aIndividualisierung. 4aKultur. 4aKunst. 4aKunstpädagogik. 4aMedien. 4aMedienwissenschaft. 4aPopkultur. 4aSelbstdarstellung. 4aSocial Media. 4aWorld of Warcraft. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Media Studies.2bisacsh  aArt Education.  aArt.  aComputer Games.  aCulture.  aEducation.  aFacebook.  aImage Theory.  aImage.  aIndividualization.  aMedia Studies.  aMedia.  aPopular Culture.  aSelf-portrait.  aSocial Media.  aVideo Games.  aVisual Studies.2 aHans-Böckler-Stiftungefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2019z978311071956708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2019z9783110606485oZDB-23-DSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.14361/9783839448502zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839448502423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783839448502.jpg  a978-3-11-071956-7  DG Plus eBook-Package 2019b2019  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2019  aZDB-23-DSWb2019